{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b629331341","title":"关于陕西凤翔县天主教堂囤积粮食问题的通报（节录）","origin":"陕西省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"debaad6043","index":0,"year":1954,"month":3,"day":2,"articleId":"b629331341"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"76e19754d7","name":"[西北局]"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"45577a261e","type":"title","text":"关于陕西凤翔县天主教堂囤积粮食问题的通报（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b629331341"},{"id":"ab7be0183b","type":"authors","text":"[西北局]","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b629331341"},{"id":"1501ca4a50","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b629331341"},{"id":"776812ab1e","type":"paragraph","text":"凤翔县天主教堂于1953年粮食市场一度紧张后，在夏收期间大肆囤积，以秘密抢购和募捐等手法共的小麦1千老石。现已查明者计购买小麦135市石；行医付账得小麦15石 4斗5升。在其购买粮食时，因正值国家夏季收购工作开始，他们为实现囤积企图，竟以每斗高出牌价1500元的办法进行抢购，并采取秘密讲价后，由售粮者夜间偷运，或借口念经，把粮食送进村舍神学院等处。… 共存粮250余石… 如此大肆囤粮是为:","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b629331341"},{"id":"8aaf0d34d5","type":"paragraph","text":"1．做投机生意，扩大教会基金。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b629331341"},{"id":"19230534d0","type":"paragraph","text":"2．在青黄不接时，出借给部分教徒群众，借以扩大宗教影响。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b629331341"},{"id":"8ded390da8","type":"paragraph","text":"3．作为宣传组织，发展宗教活动的经费。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b629331341"}],"page":{"id":"a7a21e5500","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"b629331341","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}